qStringExpression.qExpr: IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','% of Login Access available','% of unallocated Analyzer Access')

qMeasure.qDef:
Num(
IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based',
	IF(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]-[License Unavailable Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens])>0,
    	Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]-[License Unavailable Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),0)
    ,
    IF(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer*"}>}[License Total Available Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer*"}>}[License Total Tokens])>0,
    	Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer*"}>}[License Total Available Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer*"}>}[License Total Tokens]),0)
    )
,'0%')
qMeasure.qLabel: Available Login Access/ Unallocated Analyzer Access

qMetaDef.title: Available Login Access/ Unallocated Analyzer Access

materializedPath.namePath: My Qlik/Streams/Monitoring apps/License Monitor/Measures/Available Login Access\/ Unallocated Analyzer Access
